stuck-up Anne Geddes.

15:57.656 --> 16:00.716
Although, Anne did take
that great staff photo.

16:00.826 --> 16:03.624
<i>[Bullock]</i>
<i>That she did. That she did.</i>

16:03.729 --> 16:06.459
I told you to listen to me!
And now we're screwed!

16:06.565 --> 16:08.430
Relax. I'll just go fetch a lizard...

16:08.534 --> 16:11.094
tell Bullock that the alien
jumped out of you and into it...

16:11.203 --> 16:13.330
and you'll walk out
that door scot-free.

16:13.439 --> 16:16.897
That, uh, actually makes sense.

16:17.009 --> 16:19.807
Now, I'm gonna have to rough you up
a little, make it seem like...

16:19.912 --> 16:22.107
I tried to get some info from you.

16:26.552 --> 16:28.520
