16:32.191 --> 16:36.150
Hmm. Not bad.
Perfect.

16:37.463 --> 16:39.863
He's close.
I gotta take a walk to the pet store...

16:39.965 --> 16:42.559
clear my head, and then
I'll go back in and crack that mother.

16:42.668 --> 16:45.728
Uh, no need, Peters.
We're performing the autopsy now.

16:45.838 --> 16:48.898
Agent Smith will die
a horrible, painful death.

16:49.008 --> 16:51.533
But it's worth it
to finally nail this bastard.

16:51.643 --> 16:54.510
You've served your country well.

16:54.613 --> 16:56.740
Uh- Okay.

16:56.849 --> 16:58.749
It's been fun.

16:58.851 --> 17:01.445
Guess I'll just... go then.

17:01.553 --> 17:06.252
Now, we'll crack the rib cage and remove
each and every organ until we find the alien.

17:06.358 --> 17:09.088
- You're gonna die.
- What?

17:09.194 --> 17:11.094
[Sobbing]
You're right!

17:11.195 --> 17:14.063
I screwed up.
They're gonna cut you open.

17:14.165 --> 17:16.760
