17:52.671 --> 17:54.730
I'll do it, Stan.

17:56.809 --> 17:59.300
There's your alien, men!
I pooped him out!

17:59.411 --> 18:01.311
What?
You said I'd get away!

18:01.413 --> 18:03.643
You sold me out!
I trusted you!

18:03.749 --> 18:05.512
I don't know what he's talking about.

18:05.617 --> 18:08.245
He'll say anything to save his life.
We'd better cut him up immediately.

18:08.353 --> 18:10.344
No! Kill him instead!

18:10.456 --> 18:12.856
He's been harboring me!
I've been living in his-

18:12.958 --> 18:14.858
Large intestine.
It was terrible.

18:14.960 --> 18:17.394
- I thought kidney stones were bad.
- Nice work, Smith.

18:17.496 --> 18:21.455
