- [Gasps]

18:40.219 --> 18:43.814
It's the type of mackerel
the nuns used to beat the lies into you.

18:43.922 --> 18:46.322
- You're a lefty!
- No!

18:46.425 --> 18:50.384
[Sobbing]

18:50.496 --> 18:52.361
Yes. Yes, it's true!

18:52.464 --> 18:56.059
Oh! What you children
must think of me.

18:56.168 --> 19:00.104
I'll tell you what we think of you.
You're a strong, vibrant lady...

19:00.205 --> 19:02.730
